1. Oni su činili* velike stvari. (They were doing great things.)
2. Ona je činila* velike usluge narodu. (She was doing great services to the people.)
3. Oni su činili* sve što su mogli. (They were doing all they could.)
4. Činjenica* je da je ona bila veoma uspešna. (The fact is that she was very successful.)
5. Njeni činovi* su bili pohvaljeni. (Her deeds were praised.)
6. Ona je činila* velike stvari za zemlju. (She was doing great things for the country.)